description: Clearing for results, a partnership for landmind action in Cambodia

subproject.description:
(I) Improved mechanisms for funding mine clearance that promote efficiency, accountability, and the targeting of mine clearance resources on development priorities established at national, provincial and local levels;
(II) Strengthened capacities for mine action policy-making, strategy formulation and prioritization of mine clearance tasks in accordance with development priorities established at provincial and local levels.
